\cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\'93Modern moral philosophy separates moral reasoning about duties and obligations from practical reasoning about ends and practical deliberation about the means to one\'92s ends, and in doing so it separates morality from practice. Kant separates moral and practical reasoning explicitly in 
